org.cloudbus.cloudsim

Class CloudletSchedulerDynamicWorkload

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cloudbus.cloudsim.CloudletScheduler
      • org.cloudbus.cloudsim.CloudletSchedulerTimeShared
        • org.cloudbus.cloudsim.CloudletSchedulerDynamicWorkload

  • public class CloudletSchedulerDynamicWorkload
extends CloudletSchedulerTimeShared
    CloudletSchedulerDynamicWorkload implements a policy of scheduling performed by a virtual machine assuming that there is just one cloudlet which is working as an online service.
    Since:
    CloudSim Toolkit 2.0
    Author:
    Anton Beloglazov
